 PAUL PIERCE: Just taking my time, picking my spots, getting to the mid-range. Difficult to finish in the half court when you have Dwight there underneath the paint blocking the shots.  
 I'm trying to find my spot in the middle. My mid-range game, three-point game. I'm trying to work those areas. The guys are doing a good job getting me open.   
  
