 PAUL PIERCE: The difference between LeBron and anybody in the league? You are talking about a two-time MVP. He's been on the all-defensive team. Pretty much covers your whole scouting report. (Indiscernible) more so than this series. They have a couple of guys -- they don't have a two-time MVP. Not yet.   
  
