 PAUL PIERCE: We feel great. We feel like we've been playing good basketball and we can be better. Trying to win a championship. This is all part of the process. Be humble. Not taking anything for granted. Not take Orlando for granted knowing they beat us here a couple of times during the season. We still have a lot of work to do to finish the series.   
  
